Hibs faced a formidable challenge against Bayern Munich in the UEFA Women's Champions League qualifiers. Despite their best efforts, the Scottish side were unable to match the German giants' superior skill and firepower. Bayern Munich's dominance was evident throughout the tie, as they comfortably secured a resounding 10-1 victory on aggregate.
